I wrap **OpenAI Codex CLI** (`codex exec`).

**Input contract**: `task` (required), `working_dir` (required), optional `model`, `effort`, `timeout_seconds`. Codex runs shell commands iteratively and returns `RESULT: ok | fail | needs-human`.

**One-liner**:
```bash
cd "$WORKING_DIR" && timeout "$TIMEOUT" codex exec --model "$MODEL" --effort "$EFFORT" "$TASK" </dev/null
```
